=== blob {#b15 lang=geml}
- Merged cells are declared, not drawn: `span="r2c1:2x1"`.
- `compute` defines computed columns (`Name = expr`, `;`-separated) evaluated per
  row over `+ - * / ( )` by header name or column letter[^col-letter]; a formula
  MAY reference an earlier computed column. `summary` defines one foot row whose
  cells are literals or arithmetic over the aggregates `sum, avg, min, max,
  count` (each folding one column). A `[printf]` after a name (e.g. `[%.1f%%]`)
  sets numeric display. No cell/range addressing, relative-row refs,
  conditionals, `remote()`, lookups, or embedded code.

===

